# Task Management System - Git Ignore Template
# Copy this to .gitignore before creating GitHub repository

# ====================
# PERSONAL FILES (Don't Share)
# ====================

# Daily files (except templates and samples)
daily/*.md
!daily/template-*.md
!daily/*-SAMPLE.md

# Meeting notes (except templates and samples)
meetings/*.md
!meetings/template-*.md
!meetings/*-SAMPLE.md

# Weekly plans (except templates)
weekly-plans/*.md
!weekly-plans/template-*.md

# Weekly summaries (except samples)
weekly-summaries/*.md
!weekly-summaries/*-SAMPLE.md

# Decisions (keep template and samples only)
decisions/*.md
!decisions/README.md
!decisions/template-*.md
!decisions/*-SAMPLE.md

# Inbox (all personal)
inbox/*.md

# Reviews (except templates)
reviews/*.md
!reviews/template-*.md

# Projects (except templates and active project dashboard)
projects/*.md
!projects/template-*.md
!projects/ACTIVE_PROJECTS-TEMPLATE.md

