# NOTES
# ====================

# Before sharing:
# 1. Copy this to .gitignore
# 2. Review all files that will be committed: git status
# 3. Search for personal info: grep -r "your-email@" .
# 4. Create sample files with -SAMPLE suffix
# 5. Genericize memory-bank files
# 6. Test: git add . && git status (review what's being added)

